    University Student Heights

    heights.Rd

    Heights of 100 randomly selected male university students from Table 2.1 of Spiegel and Stephens (2008).

    Usage

    heights

    Format

    An integer vector with length 100.

    heights

    Height of the student in inches.

    Source

    Adapted from Spiegel, Murray R., and Larry J. Stephens, (2008). Theory and Problems of Statistics. 4th edn. McGraw-Hill. ISBN:9780071755498

    See also: https://brownmath.com
